{"tid":1610274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論］點解要破壞燈柱","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:04:26.000Z","uid":7969,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2143732b43b1666fec2d961f6eac1a9c802b4bb0","tid":1610274,"uid":7969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:54:01.000Z","msg":"明白大家都好仇恨香港政府同警察<br />\n<br />\n我相信大家都係愛香港哩個地方先會去到今時今日都繼續行落去<br />\n<br />\n破壞黨鐵、優品我都明白，起碼出師有名<br />\n<br />\n但係非智能既普通燈柱？係咪有必要性？如果係鬼，咁又係咪應該有人當場阻止/問佢動機？<br />\n<br />\n利申：希望大家討論下係咪需要瞄準返訴求同政權做事，而唔係拎住不分化不割蓆就做想做既野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qDK85a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqDK85a3.png&h=3faf246a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B2_yzUagwse/?igshid=4qw6ar5fo0y6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2_yzUagwse%2F%3Figshid%3D4qw6ar5fo0y6&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=69e63379\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB2_yzUagwse%2F%3Figshid%3D4qw6ar5fo0y6&h=990fe15a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B2_yzUagwse/?igshid=4qw6ar5fo0y6</a>"},{"pid":"c95a4e9221a897b03a2657240b9aef84a351b482","tid":1610274,"uid":7969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"推 有無人討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e53ae28eb44d497a010d0be9305ece3cad9b2c6","tid":1610274,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拆政府野有咩問題"},{"pid":"8fb737986594c3e227dbf6a080638c8986ac9d4b","tid":1610274,"uid":133363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}